            <abstract>
                <p>Prayer against haemorrhaging, invoking the words ‘lis ʾaflis mali wa-malalis’ as ʾasmāt, which are also used in various other
                    magic prayers against haemorrhage, as for instance in <ref type="work" corresp="LIT6488PPDam"/>, 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT6814MagicPr"/> and <ref type="work" corresp="LIT6844PPHemorrhage"/>.
                    It is possibly a continuation of <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7767PPAlef"/>, which is attested in the same manuscript
                    immediately before.</p>
